### Create a New Comment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "targetType": "video",
  "targetId": 5,
  "content": "Wow, Gio was on fire this game!"
}

### Retrieve All Comments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/comments

### Retrieve a Specific Comment (Assume ID is 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/comments/1

### Update an Existing Comment
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/comments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "targetType": "video",
  "targetId": 5,
  "content": "Updated comment: Even better upon a second watch!"
}

### Delete a Comment
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/comments/1
